Package com.example.team04adventure.Model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Choice
    Class that models a choice associated with a fragment item.
    ElasticSearchResponse<T>
    ElasticSearchResponse gets the response from ElasticSearch.
    ElasticSearchSearchResponse<T>
    ElasticSearchSearchResponse gets the return type of ElasticSearchResponse.
    Frag
    Frag is meant to contain the id, title, body, and related media of a single story fragment inside a single object.
    FragAdapter
    FragAdapter is an adapter to get the list of fragments.
    FragChoiceAdapter
    FragChoiceAdapter is an adapter to get the fragment choice list.
    Hits<T>
    Hits gets the response from ElasticSearchResponse.
    JSONparser
    JSONparser deals with the storage on the server.
    Media
    Media holds the images, videos, and sounds that can be associated to any fragment.
    SQLiteHelper
    SQLiteHelper is meant to handle required SQLite operations that the user does not have access to.
    StorageManager
    StorageManager is meant to write data into the SQLite database.
    Story
    Story is meant to create and hold the ID, title, author and all associated fragments of a story.
    StoryListAdapter
    StoryListAdapter is an adapter to get the story list.
